==============================================
Magazine apps for Android and iPhone/iPad/iPod
==============================================

If you own an Android phone or tablet, or an iPhone, iPad or iPod Touch, you can read New Internationalist magazine in our native apps. Use the same login details you have for digital.newint.com.au and read articles offline, and also send articles to your friends to read (even if they don't have a subscription).

Download the Android app:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=au.com.newint.newinternationalist

Download the iPhone, iPad & iPod Touch app:
https://itunes.apple.com/au/app/new-internationalist-magazine/id711254931?mt=8&uo=4